sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant DB
    participant SQS_completion_check
    participant AsyncWorker as Async Worker

    Client->>API: POST /storeCheckins (payload)
    API-->>DB: write step data
    API->>SQS_completion_check: publish completion check event
    API-->>Client: 204 No Content

    Note over SQS_completion_check,AsyncWorker: async worker consumes later
